results.title: Bright & Bubbly Cardigan
results.description:
This is a great knit cardigan in a beautiful bright blue. The buttons are a smokey blueish-gray. The open knit pattern on the shoulders trails down the cardigan into small knit stripes for an interesting and delicate detail.

Pair this cardigan over a light colored spring dress with some great wedges, or some grey denim and a colorful patterned top. It will look great with anything!

Excellent vintage condition! There are no original size tags, but it fits like a small.

Bust: 34 in

results.title: Fruity Flowy Cardigan
results.description:
Pineapples, berries, and vines... oh my! This cardigan is a cropped, loose fitting flirty style. The fabric is sheer, with cream colored shoulders and a berry colored body. The pattern makes great use of the negative space by the shoulders. The cream color fades into the bottom as the blouse is taken over by red berries, fruit on the vine, and tiny pineapples.

Pair this cardigan with a cream colored dress and some gladiator sandals for a boho, flirty style. Wear it over a bandeau for a sexy hippie style. Or just wear it with your favorite skinny jeans for an easy look that is all your own.

Excellent vintage condition! Fits like a size small or medium because it is an loose open fit, but there are no signs of any original tags to be found (possibly handmade?).

Measures approx.
Shoulder: 16 in across
Bust: 40 in
Sleeve: 21 1/2 in
Length: 23 in

results.title: Elegant Oval Serving Tray
results.description:
Beautiful vintage silver-plated serving tray. 

This tray is stamped with an elegant flower and filigree design. Bottom surface is smooth, with a polished finish.

In excellent vintage condition! No dings, dents, or nics. The only visible damage are some very small scratches on the bottom of the tray.

This item would make a great vanity tray, housewarming gift, or wall decoration! Such a lovely way to store your cosmetics, perfumes, jewelry, or other small collections.
